entry.title: What establishments can operate in areas under GCQ? | Teleradyo

media:group.media:title: What establishments can operate in areas under GCQ? | Teleradyo
media:group.media:description: Presidential Spokesman Harry Roque enumerated establishments which can operate in areas under general community quarantine. Metro Manila, the provinces of Rizal, Laguna, Bulacan and Cavite transitioned to GCQ from the stricter modified enhanced community quarantine (MECQ) on Wednesday.
